      • setDelayIndex

        public void setDelayIndex(int delayIndex)
        For delay arc nodes, this will set the delay value for the arc (same field as the wire field). If this is not a delay arc, no action will take place.
        Parameters:
        delayIndex - The delay to set

      • getDelayIndex

        public int getDelayIndex()
        If this is delay arc node, it will return the current delay arc value setting. It will cause a runtime exception if this method is called on a non-delay arc node.
        Returns:
        The value of the delay setting for this delay arc node.
